dct_description_sm: Relief shown by landform drawing. Shows southern limit of glaciation in Indiana. Originally compiled approximately 1932 by J.E. Switzer, Department of Geology and Geography, Indiana University. Detached from: Kingsbury, Robert C. Atlas of Indiana, page 15. Scale approximately 1,850,000
